SUMMARY:In the Kingdom of Fungi
DESCRIPTION:From life-saving medicines to deadly toxins; from mind-bending chemicals to the nourishment on our plates. \nEmbarrassingly\, we know so little about fungi. \nThis session invites you to watch\, listen\, and participate. Three short films\, a panel discussion with entrepreneurs and experts\, and a light-hearted audience interaction with quizzes\, polls and surprises. \nThis event is a part of the Environment Day programming at BIC. \nIn Collaboration with: \n \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/in-the-kingdom-of-fungi/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Environment,Film,Wildlife
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Thumbnail-10-2.jpg
END:VEVENT
